<heading label="H1" alternateLabel="Basic Info Header" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Basic Information Setup</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T1" style="normal"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="D50000"><b><i><field name="Message"/></i></b></font></paragraph></text>
<text label="T2" style="normal"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><b>Set up Administrator:  </b></font><font><i>(This is the </i></font><font><i><u>only </u></i></font><font><i>person who will have access to this Setup screen.  Other members of the leadership are set up below and may have some or all other Administrator privileges, as you designate)</i></font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q1" style="rightAlignLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Name:  </font><blank label="a" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="AdminsName"/></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Email Address:  </font><blank label="b" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="AdminsEmail"/></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Phone Number: </font><blank label="c" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="AdminPhone"/></paragraph></fib>
<text label="T3" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>A password is not necessary.  However,  you may wish to add a password to ensure </font><font><b>Setup Administrator </b></font><font>security.</font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q2" style="rightAlignLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Personal Password: </font><blank label="a" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="AdminPass"/></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Please enter again: </font><blank label="b" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="PasswordCheck"/></paragraph></fib>
<text label="T4" style="normal"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><b>Basic Organization Information:</b></font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q3" style="rightAlignLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Organization Name: </font><blank label="a" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="ClubName"/></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Contact Phone: </font><blank label="b" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="ClubPhone"/></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Contact Email: </font><blank label="c" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="ClubEmail"/></paragraph></fib>
<fib label="Q4" style="rightAlignLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Website URL: </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(if any)</i></font><sp/><blank label="a" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="ClubURL"/></paragraph></fib>
<text label="T5" style="normal"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><b>Membership:</b></font></paragraph></text>
<text label="T6" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Some organizations maintain data on multiple, sometimes overlapping categories of people,  such as parents, alumni, and local business leaders, all of whom are to be included in financial campaigns and certain communications.  Different information may be maintained on people in different categories, and they may have different levels of activity or involvement as well.  For example, one might maintain information on local business leaders for solicitation purposes, but not offer them membership dashboards, which are used to give members communications capabilities and access to a broad range of reports.</font></paragraph></text>
<mc label="Q5" alternateLabel="Categories?" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Do you wish to set up such multiple categories in the membership database?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">No</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q6" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Will you be employing online membership registration?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">No, we already have our membership list and will add any new ones manually</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<text label="T7" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Many organizations also create committees or task forces to involve their membership in specific activities.  These committees often have separate leadership, and members of such committees are given a range of communication and other tools tied to their committee participation.</font></paragraph></text>
<mc label="Q7" alternateLabel="Committees?" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Do you wish to create and manage committees?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">No</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<skipInstructions>
<if>
<conditions>
<doesNotEqual field="AdminSetup:AdminPass">
<string field="AdminSetup:PasswordCheck"/>
</doesNotEqual>
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<set field="Message" arithmeticAsText="false">
<string value="Your two passwords don&apos;t match."/>
</set>
<skip to="Basic Info Header"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
<if>
<conditions>
<isNotBlank field="SetupNavigation" />
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="__EndOfForm__"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
<if>
<conditions>
<mcEquals field="AdminSetup:Q6" value="b"/>
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="Leadership Header"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</skipInstructions>
<heading label="H2" alternateLabel="Registration Header" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Online Registration Form Setup</font></paragraph></heading>
<fib label="Q8" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Header text: </font><blank label="a" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="RegFormHeader"/></paragraph></fib>
<fib label="Q9" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Sub-header text </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(optional)</i></font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">: </font><blank label="a" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="RegFormSubHeader"/></paragraph></fib>
<fib label="Q10" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Additional descriptive text </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(optional):</i></font><sp/><blank label="a" length="35" required="false" alternateLabel="Description"/></paragraph></fib>
<text label="T8" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><i>Note: The above Header, Sub-header and descriptive text appear at the top of the Registration Form, and can contain any information you would like to have appear there.</i></font></paragraph></text>
<skipInstructions>
<if>
<conditions>
<isNotBlank field="SetupNavigation" />
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="__EndOfForm__"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</skipInstructions>
<heading label="H3" alternateLabel="Leadership Header" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Leadership Records Setup</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T9" style="normal"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><b>Optional Items</b></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><i>Place a check next to items you want to include in your leadership profiles.</i></font></paragraph></text>
<mc label="Q11" alternateLabel="LeadershipPublicContacts" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Include the following in public profiles </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(visible to all members):</i></font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Work phone</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Home phone</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Mobile phone</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="d"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Email address</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="e"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Physical address</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q12" alternateLabel="LeadershipPrivateContacts" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Includes the following in leadership profiles (</font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>visible to Club's leadership group) </i></font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Work phone</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Home phone</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Mobile phone</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="d"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Email address</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="e"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Physical address</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<skipInstructions>
<if>
<conditions>
<isNotBlank field="SetupNavigation" />
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="__EndOfForm__"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</skipInstructions>
<heading label="H4" alternateLabel="Membership Header" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Membership Records Setup</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T10" alternateLabel="Phone Descriptions1" style="normal"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000000"><b>Phone Descriptions: </b></font><font color="000000"><i>(Enter name you would like each phone field described as, e.g. Dad's Mobile, Home phone, etc.)</i></font></paragraph></text>
<fib label="Q13" style="leftAlignLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">   Phone 1: </font><blank label="a" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="PhonA1"/></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">   Phone 2: </font><blank label="b" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="PhonB1"/></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">   Phone 3: </font><blank label="c" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="PhonC1"/></paragraph></fib>
<text label="T11" style="normal"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><b>Optional Items</b></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><i>Place a check next to items you want to include in your membership database:</i></font></paragraph></text>
<mc label="Q14" alternateLabel="SecondParentName" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Second Parent Name</font></paragraph></choice><displayConditions>
<equals field="AskSecondParentName">
<string value="Yes"/>
</equals>
</displayConditions></mc>
<mc label="Q15" alternateLabel="SecondParentAddress" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Second Parent Address</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q16" alternateLabel="SecondParentEmail" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Second Parent Email</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q17" alternateLabel="Children&apos;s Names" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Children's Names </font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q18" alternateLabel="SchoolName" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Children's School(s)</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q19" alternateLabel="SchoolGrade" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Children's School Grade </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(You will set up grades later.)</i></font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q20" alternateLabel="SchoolActivities" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Children's School Activities </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(You will set these up later - they can be tied to parent committee or volunteer activity categories)</i></font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<skipInstructions>
<if>
<conditions>
<isNotBlank field="SetupNavigation" />
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="__EndOfForm__"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</skipInstructions>
<heading label="H5" alternateLabel="GroupHeader" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Membership Setup</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T12" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><i>(You will set these groups up later.)</i></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>The "Membership Groups" option allows you to form committees or sub-groups out of your membership (such as "</font><font><i>Football Team Boosters</i></font><font>" or "</font><font><i>Fundraising Committee</i></font><font>") and then either have registrants volunteer for them or permit the leadership to assign members.  You can also tie certain children's activities (such as "</font><font><i>Plays on football team</i></font><font>") to specific groups.</font></paragraph></text>
<mc label="Q21" alternateLabel="VolunteerQuestions" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">How will members of these groups be selected?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Members of all groups assigned by leadership</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Members of  groups will be invited to volunteer or identify themselves on registration form</font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i> (if any)</i></font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"> or by email</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<fib label="Q22" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Generic name for a group: </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(e.g. Club, Committee, Team)</i></font><sp/><blank label="a" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="CollectiveGroupName"/></paragraph></fib>
<mc label="Q23" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Will these groups have an indicated leader?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">No</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<fib label="Q24" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Leadership name: </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(e.g.Head, Leader, Director)</i></font><sp/><blank label="a" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="GroupLdrCollName"/></paragraph></fib>
<skipInstructions>
<if>
<conditions>
<isNotBlank field="SetupNavigation" />
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="__EndOfForm__"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</skipInstructions>
<heading label="H6" alternateLabel="FundraisingHeader" type="Sub"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="360" color="000000">Dues &amp; Fundraising Setup</font></paragraph></heading>
<text label="T13" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Dues</font></paragraph></text>
<mc label="Q25" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Does this organization require its membership to pay annual contributions or "dues"?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">No</font></paragraph></choice><displayConditions>
<mcEquals field="AdminSetup:Categories?">
<string value="b"/>
</mcEquals>
</displayConditions></mc>
<mc label="Q26" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Does this organization require its membership to pay annual contributions or "dues"?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes, all members are charged</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Only some categories of membership are charged</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">No</font></paragraph></choice><displayConditions>
<mcEquals field="AdminSetup:Categories?" value="a"/>
</displayConditions></mc>
<fib label="Q27" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">What are annual required contributions called (i.e. dues, fees, etc)? </font><blank label="a" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="DuesName"/></paragraph></fib>
<mc label="Q28" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Are all annual member contributions the same amount?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">No, they can vary</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<skipInstructions>
<if>
<conditions>
<mcEquals field="AdminSetup:Q28" value="b"/>
</conditions>
<trueSet>
<skip to="T14"/>
</trueSet>
</if>
</skipInstructions>
<fib label="Q29" style="topLabels"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Set initial  </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><field name="AdminSetup:DuesName"/></font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">: $</font><blank label="a" length="20" required="false" alternateLabel="Dues"/></paragraph></fib>
<break/>
<text label="T14" style="instructional"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Fundraising Campaigns</font></paragraph></text>
<mc label="Q30" onlyone="false" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Which of the following may have separate campaign targets </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(check as many as apply)</i></font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">the </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><field name="Club"/></font><sp/></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">a category of membership </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(if membership categories are used)</i></font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">the </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><field name="BossGroup"/></font><sp/></paragraph></choice><choice label="d"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">some or all of the </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><field name="GroupCollectiveName"/></font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">s </font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<mc label="Q31" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Who is responsible for establishing and tracking campaign targets</font></paragraph></question><data-provider><dynamic-mcq version="1"><display-expression><field name="Record:LeaderNames:First"/>
<string value=" "/>
<field name="Record:LeaderNames:Last"/>
<string value=" ("/>
<field name="Record:LeaderNames:PositionName"/>
<string value=")"/>
</display-expression><value-expression><field name="Record:LeaderNames:NameID"/>
</value-expression><sort-expression></sort-expression><record-selector><form name="LeaderNames" /></record-selector></dynamic-mcq></data-provider></mc>
<mc label="Q32" onlyone="true" required="false" style="vertical"><question><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Will you use track pledges for some or all of your campaigns?</font></paragraph></question><choice label="a"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes, one time pledges</font></paragraph></choice><choice label="b"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">Yes, duration based pledges </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><i>(e.g. $10/month)</i></font></paragraph></choice><choice label="c"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">No</font></paragraph></choice></mc>
<field name="CollectiveLeadership"/>
<field name="MemberIDGenerator"/>
<field name="RecruitmentIDGenerator"/>
</items>
</form>
