<document name="RecruitmentMgmt">
<xmlData>
<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font size="280">Manage the Recruitment List</font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="MasterAdminDash" project="">Back to Dashboard</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><table indent="255"><row><cell width="3495"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="ShowRecruitDB" project="">View recruitment list</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="272"></cell><cell width="3223"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="AddRecruitRecord" project="">Add a recruitment record</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="3555"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="RecruitEmail" project="">Send email to recruitment list</invitation></u></font></division></cell></row><row><cell width="3495"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="AuditRecruitList" project="">Audit recruitment email addresses</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="272"></cell><cell width="3223"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="EditRecruitment" project="">Edit a recruitment record</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="3555"></cell></row><row><cell width="3495"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="DuplicateRecruitCheck" project="">Check for duplicate records</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="272"></cell><cell width="3223"><division indent="0" align="left"><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="DeleteRecruitment" project="">Delete a recruitment record</invitation></u></font></division></cell><cell width="3555"></cell></row></table><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="004000">You can  manage records in the Recruitment List both here and on the Tawala Website in your MyProjects Project Detail Page. The recruitment list is called "RecruitmentDB."  It is easier to delete records from the Web page, and you can also import contact lists there.  To import, try clicking on the import icon (</font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><image id="image1" width="26" height="22"><metafileHeader fileType="1" headerSize="9" version="768" fileSize="933" numOfObjects="0" maxRecordSize="911" numOfParams="0" />
</image></font><font color="004000">) to the right of "RecruitmentDB" file name and select an Excel or .csv file to import. The file must have the correct information in these four fields: </font><font color="004000"><i>First Name, Last Name, Email address, Phone.</i></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="004000"><i><link-to-project-details version="1"><description><string value="Jump to MyTawala Project Detail Page"/>
</description><open-preference>new-window</open-preference></link-to-project-details></i></font></paragraph>
</xmlData>
</document>
<document name="RecruitDB">
<xmlData>
<paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font color="000080"><u><invitation form="Recruitment" project="">Return to Recruitment</invitation></u></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font>Number of records: </font><font><record-count version="3"><form-name>RecruitmentDB</form-name><conditions><form name="RecruitmentDB" /></conditions></record-count></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="2880"/></tabPositions><font><itemization-table version="2"><show-print-control>false</show-print-control><column><header><string value="First Name"/>
</header><contents><field name="Record:RecruitmentDB:FirstName" /></contents></column><column><header><string value="Last Name"/>
